title: Found
overview: Every day, people are finding unexplained objects in their own backyards across America. Now, for the first time, a group of experts is fanning out across the nation to investigate tips of these strange discoveries. They study the objects, test them, date them, and deliver real answers about the origins of people's most intriguing finds.
